This PR refactors duplicated JSON serialization logic used by the normal and log_normal distributions in:

FIMS/inst/include/interface/rcpp/rcpp_objects/rcpp_distribution.hpp

Both implementations currently contain nearly identical code except for the "module_type" field ("normal" vs "log_normal"). Maintaining duplicate implementations increases the maintenance burden and makes future distribution extensions more difficult.

This PR extracts the shared JSON serialization logic into a reusable helper function called build_density_json. The distribution type is passed as a parameter, eliminating duplication while keeping the generated JSON output identical.

No functional changes are introduced.
